{"title":"闽南行","authors":["陈沂"],"dates":[{"year":1982,"month":12,"day":24}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"闽南行"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"陈沂"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十一月下旬，乘在福建开会之便，有闽南之行，伫立海边，感叹不已，赋此纪行，并遥寄台湾同胞，但求抒情言志，不计韵律工整。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"过泉州"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"泉州自古称大港"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“涨海声中万国商”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"而今国策倡开放"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"振兴八闽寄侨乡"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"观古船"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"古船沉沙七百年"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"炎黄子孙功盖天"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"闽南儿女今赛古"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敢教侨乡翻两番"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"望金门"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"厦门金门两相对"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大陆台湾一家人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"碧海蓝天隔不断"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"梦中犹作故乡行"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"访陈嘉庚先生故居"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"抗战建国常系心"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"力排众议陕北行"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"肝胆相照从兹定"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"爱国侨胞第一人"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}